<div class="container bg-info-subtle col-xxl-8 px-4 py-5">
    <div class="row flex-lg-row-reverse align-items-center g-5 py-5">
      <div class="col-10 col-sm-8 col-lg-6">
        <img src="<%= asset_url 'schoolyard.png' %>" class="d-block mx-lg-auto img-fluid" alt="cartoon children in front of school house" width="700" height="500" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3">Improving communication between educators and parents</h1>
        <p class="lead">SchoolYard is a messaging app with built-in event notification and calendar to keep studentsâ€™ parents informed about their activities. Better communication leads to greater parent engagement, which leads to better educational outcomes for their children.</p>
      </div>
        <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row align-items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 me-3">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-desktop"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="display-6 mb-1">Event Creation and Group Notification</h2>
            <p>Create events in a snap, and let SchoolYard instantly notify group members.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 me-3">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="display-6 mb-1">Built-in Calendar</h2>
            <p>No more copying and pasting from a separate document!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 me-3">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-comments"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="display-6 mb-1">Targeted Messaging</h2>
            <p>Respects privacy and security, allowing users to focus on the educational activities that matter most. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="display-6 fw-bold lh-1 mb-3">SchoolYard is great for:</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-success me-2"></i>Schools</li>
              <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-success me-2"></i>Sports clubs at all levels</li>
              <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check text-success me-2"></i>Day care centers</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-start">
          <div class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 me-md-2">
            <%= link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_registration_path, class: 'text-white' %>
          </div>
          <div class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4">
            <%= link_to 'Log In', new_user_session_path, class: 'text-dark' %>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
